Maybe to put more in perspective:1) If SA > FRS  FRS amount will be parked into RA for CPF Life. Thereafter  any access in SA and OA can be withdrawn respective order.2) If SA < FRS  whatever is in SA will be moved to RA followed by balance amount from OA to RA in order to fulfill the FRS to parked into RA for CPF Life.3) The instant ATM will be withdrawn from SA first and then followed by OA. Unless u fulfilled point 1) and done ur shielding
